  "title": "Assistant Civil Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Description:-</strong></u></p><p>1. Knowledge of DCM operational and functional (Preferred).</p><p>2. Responsible for the planning and coordination of development works, etc</p><p>3. Daily inspection, method statement, supervise quality control, etc</p><p>4. Production planning and control</p><p>5. Able to work in team and independently</p><p>6. Assisting Project Manager / Project Engineer</p><p>7. Will be stationed on site</p><p>8. Knowledge of Construction industries</p><p>9. Priority for work with LTA documentation</p><p><br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Requirement:-</strong></u></p><p>1. Bachelor/Master Degree in Civil Engineering from recognized Institution.</p><p>2. Min 1 - 2 years of practical experiences in related industries preferred. (Construction)</p><p>3. Able to work long hours, 6 days week</p><p>Working hours: 7am – 7pm.</p><p>4. Proficient in AutoCAD</p>",
